<% content_for :title, "Community Guidelines - Travel Planner" %>

<div class="container my-5">
  <div class="row justify-content-center">
    <div class="col-lg-10">
      <div class="card shadow">
        <div class="card-header bg-primary text-white">
          <h1 class="h2 mb-0">Community Guidelines</h1>
          <p class="mb-0 mt-2">Building a Safe and Respectful Travel Community</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="card-body">
          <div class="alert alert-info">
            <strong>Last Updated:</strong> December 2025
          </div>
          
          <section class="mb-5">
            <h2 class="h4 border-bottom pb-2 mb-3">Our Commitment</h2>
            <p>
              Travel Planner is committed to creating a safe, inclusive, and respectful environment for all travelers. 
              These guidelines help ensure that our community remains a positive space for everyone to share experiences, 
              seek advice, and plan their adventures.
            </p>
          </section>

          <section class="mb-5">
            <h2 class="h4 border-bottom pb-2 mb-3">Core Principles</h2>
            <div class="row">
              <div class="col-md-6 mb-3">
                <div class="card h-100 border-primary">
                  <div class="card-body">
                    <h5 class="card-title text-primary">ü§ù Respect</h5>
                    <p class="card-text">Treat all community members with kindness and respect, regardless of their background, experience level, or travel preferences.</p>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="col-md-6 mb-3">
                <div class="card h-100 border-success">
                  <div class="card-body">
                    <h5 class="card-title text-success">‚úÖ Authenticity</h5>
                    <p class="card-text">Share genuine experiences and honest recommendations. Misleading information can impact others' travel plans.</p>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="col-md-6 mb-3">
                <div class="card h-100 border-info">
                  <div class="card-body">
                    <h5 class="card-title text-info">üõ°Ô∏è Safety</h5>
                    <p class="card-text">Prioritize the safety and privacy of yourself and others. Never share sensitive personal information publicly.</p>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="col-md-6 mb-3">
                <div class="card h-100 border-warning">
                  <div class="card-body">
                    <h5 class="card-title text-warning">üåç Inclusivity</h5>
                    <p class="card-text">Welcome diverse perspectives and cultures. Travel brings us together across boundaries.</p>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </section>

          <section class="mb-5">
            <h2 class="h4 border-bottom pb-2 mb-3">Prohibited Conduct</h2>
            <p>The following behaviors are strictly prohibited and may result in account suspension or termination:</p>
            
            <div class="list-group mb-3">
              <div class="list-group-item">
                <h5 class="mb-1">‚ùå Harassment & Hate Speech</h5>
                <p class="mb-1">No harassment, bullying, hate speech, discrimination, or threats based on race, ethnicity, religion, gender, sexual orientation, disability, or any other protected characteristic.</p>
              </div>
              
              <div class="list-group-item">
                <h5 class="mb-1">‚ùå Inappropriate Content</h5>
                <p class="mb-1">No sexually explicit content, graphic violence, or other content that would be inappropriate for a travel planning platform.</p>
              </div>
              
              <div class="list-group-item">
                <h5 class="mb-1">‚ùå Spam & Scams</h5>
                <p class="mb-1">No spam, phishing attempts, fraudulent schemes, or unauthorized commercial promotion. Genuine travel recommendations are welcome, but pure advertising is not.</p>
              </div>
              
              <div class="list-group-item">
                <h5 class="mb-1">‚ùå Profanity & Offensive Language</h5>
                <p class="mb-1">While we understand emotions can run high during travel disruptions, excessive profanity and offensive language are not permitted.</p>
              </div>
              
              <div class="list-group-item">
                <h5 class="mb-1">‚ùå Misinformation</h5>
                <p class="mb-1">Deliberately sharing false or misleading information about destinations, safety conditions, visa requirements, or travel restrictions.</p>
              </div>
              
              <div class="list-group-item">
                <h5 class="mb-1">‚ùå Privacy Violations</h5>
                <p class="mb-1">Sharing others' personal information (doxxing), contact details, or private messages without consent.</p>
              </div>
              
              <div class="list-group-item">
                <h5 class="mb-1">‚ùå Illegal Activities</h5>
                <p class="mb-1">Promoting or facilitating illegal activities, including but not limited to drug trafficking, human trafficking, or travel to prohibited locations.</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </section>

          <section class="mb-5">
            <h2 class="h4 border-bottom pb-2 mb-3">Best Practices</h2>
            <ul class="list-unstyled">
              <li class="mb-2">‚úÖ <strong>Be Helpful:</strong> Share your knowledge and experiences to help fellow travelers.</li>
              <li class="mb-2">‚úÖ <strong>Be Constructive:</strong> If you disagree with advice, explain why respectfully and offer alternatives.</li>
              <li class="mb-2">‚úÖ <strong>Cite Sources:</strong> When sharing travel advisories or restrictions, link to official sources.</li>
              <li class="mb-2">‚úÖ <strong>Update Information:</strong> Travel information changes quickly. Update your posts if conditions change.</li>
              <li class="mb-2">‚úÖ <strong>Respect Cultural Differences:</strong> Be mindful that travel customs and expectations vary worldwide.</li>
              <li class="mb-2">‚úÖ <strong>Protect Privacy:</strong> Don't share specific accommodation addresses or other location details that could compromise safety.</li>
            </ul>
          </section>

          <section class="mb-5">
            <h2 class="h4 border-bottom pb-2 mb-3">Content Moderation</h2>
            <p>
              Our platform uses a combination of automated systems and human review to maintain community standards:
            </p>
            <ul>
              <li><strong>Automated Filtering:</strong> Profanity and inappropriate content are automatically detected and filtered.</li>
              <li><strong>Rate Limiting:</strong> To prevent spam and abuse, certain actions have usage limits.</li>
              <li><strong>Community Reports:</strong> Users can report content that violates these guidelines.</li>
              <li><strong>Manual Review:</strong> Our team reviews reported content and takes appropriate action.</li>
            </ul>
          </section>

          <section class="mb-5">
            <h2 class="h4 border-bottom pb-2 mb-3">Reporting Violations</h2>
            <p>
              If you encounter content or behavior that violates these guidelines, please report it immediately:
            </p>
            <ol>
              <li>Click the "Report" button on the content in question</li>
              <li>Select the reason for your report</li>
              <li>Provide specific details about the violation</li>
              <li>Our team will review your report within 24-48 hours</li>
            </ol>
            <p class="alert alert-warning">
              <strong>Note:</strong> False or malicious reports may result in action against your account.
            </p>
          </section>

          <section class="mb-5">
            <h2 class="h4 border-bottom pb-2 mb-3">Enforcement</h2>
            <p>Violations of these guidelines may result in:</p>
            <ul>
              <li><strong>Warning:</strong> First-time minor violations may receive a warning.</li>
              <li><strong>Content Removal:</strong> Violating content will be removed from the platform.</li>
              <li><strong>Temporary Suspension:</strong> Repeated or serious violations may result in temporary account suspension.</li>
              <li><strong>Permanent Ban:</strong> Severe or persistent violations will result in permanent account termination.</li>
              <li><strong>Legal Action:</strong> Illegal activities will be reported to appropriate authorities.</li>
            </ul>
          </section>

          <section class="mb-5">
            <h2 class="h4 border-bottom pb-2 mb-3">Changes to Guidelines</h2>
            <p>
              We may update these guidelines from time to time to reflect changes in our community or legal requirements. 
              Continued use of the platform after changes constitutes acceptance of the updated guidelines.
            </p>
          </section>

          <section>
            <h2 class="h4 border-bottom pb-2 mb-3">Questions?</h2>
            <p>
              If you have questions about these guidelines or need to report a serious issue, please contact us.
            </p>
          </section>
        </div>
        
        <div class="card-footer text-center">
          <%= link_to "Back to Home", root_path, class: "btn btn-primary" %>
          <%= link_to "Terms of Service", terms_of_service_path, class: "btn btn-outline-secondary" %>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
